  "title": "CONSTRUCTION SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Supervise daily site activities to ensure works comply with approved drawings, specifications, and method statements.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate manpower, subcontractors, materials, and equipment to meet project schedule.</p></li><li><p>Conduct daily quality checks and arrange rectification works; follow up on defect closure.</p></li><li><p>Enforce WSH requirements: PPE compliance, toolbox briefings, safe work procedures, housekeeping.</p></li><li><p>Track progress, submit daily/weekly updates with photos and site records.</p></li><li><p>Liaise with Project Manager, consultants, subcontractors and suppliers for site coordination and inspections.</p></li></ul>",
